{"tid":1689204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<創業行動> 回收糞便、廚餘 （唔好掟POPO）","createTime":"2019-11-02T17:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T03:44:13.000Z","uid":120404,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"977155c02a48b974e8165d922833390f62ff2d4d","tid":1689204,"uid":120404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"小弟受不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意的POPO激發啓蒙，打算創業：每次大型活動利用人多之便，收集<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">人多之</span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">便</span></span>，以及大量過期廚餘，進行發電的商業研究，環保拯救地球。<br />\n<br />\n創業成功，將會天價回收，所以想發達，由今日開始，用多重密實膠袋儲存好，確保唔漏氣、唔漏便 可回收作研究之用。<br />\n<br />\n每星期如有大型活動，帶到附近回收點，以加速我哋成功研發。<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：千祈千祈千祈唔好用尼掟，亦都千祈千祈唔好交比會掟POPO嘅暴徒，因為密實膠袋裝滿可以掟好遠，仲有一掟就爆，掟中會臭幾日，仲會令POPO出臭國際。<br />\n<br />\n人多，才有人多之便，目標要夠大量，引起國際話題，延續香港人革命革新精神，家下我哋發電丫嘛。<br />\n<br />\n帶廚餘、便便去回收，不會構成藏有攻擊性武器罪，就算POPO屈你，就算要上法庭上都唔會入到罪。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有人用尼掟POPO，雖然<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">入罪比掟汽油彈輕，效果比掟𥖁大</span></span>，因為心理上極具侮辱意味，不過千祈千祈千祈唔好掟POPO，因為佢哋曾宣誓，滿身是屎都不畏懼、不徇私、不對你懷惡意的好警察。<br />\n<br />\n業務名稱已初步定為：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「時革發電」</span></span><br />\n公司宗旨：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「人多之便，時革發電」</span>"},{"pid":"6a89cecd2f6e734f603723e5be76ebd1653d68ad","tid":1689204,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c64ce038b6a43987482908af516030d9009ae6","tid":1689204,"uid":120404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"想創業"},{"pid":"cbaaf7c3511e2cba4add8bd0805bfa08c2e20876","tid":1689204,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"17d2d31cefaf5b77fee6596be45c95889a901b2a","tid":1689204,"uid":120404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"傷害一兩個POPO有為，不如一齊發電！"},{"pid":"2f1fe28b33a7d245353405605f0324d7036dd18a","tid":1689204,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:19:27.000Z","msg":"老人院附近既垃圾站通常好多屎片"},{"pid":"aa4d795e781be104abb1f80e3a43da9e64f3ef65","tid":1689204,"uid":41290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:21:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8af300e7f7e39304fdd7a292fc4f84b72dbed177","tid":1689204,"uid":120404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f1fe28b33a7d245353405605f0324d7036dd18a","tid":1689204,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:19:27.000Z","msg":"老人院附近既垃圾站通常好多屎片"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"用自己嗰啲安全D<br />\n廚餘都得<br />\n目標：集便成球"},{"pid":"8c538011e72d6a500e50f1366e148ac6b53f7454","tid":1689204,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:22:42.000Z","msg":"我驚佢哋爭嚟食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d94fc770fa25c3034b3982f28912a7e18829be","tid":1689204,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8229221b8494930be3a073aa5c2e196fae961f","tid":1689204,"uid":239469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c7175e132b6ef702f293e8f759476bd4618f96","tid":1689204,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:25:44.000Z","msg":"催淚彈疑撃中消防車消防員不滿 與警員理論時反被包圍 - RTHK <br />\n(記者再再再再次被針對及阻礙採訪)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/ceb12\" data-sr-url=\"htt